# Python Mini Projects

This repository contains simple beginner-level Python projects created as part of my self-learning journey.

## Projects Included

### 1. To-Do List
A simple command-line task manager that allows users to:
- Add tasks
- View tasks
- Remove tasks

### 2. Calculator
A basic calculator that performs:
- Addition
- Subtraction
- Multiplication
- Division

## Technologies Used
- Python (Basic concepts)
- Functions
- Loops
- Conditional Statements
